    "Participants were asked to estimate the percentage of dots that moved from left to right on a scale ranging from 0% left to right to 100% left to right, as well as to indicate their confidence on a scale ranging from not confident at all to very confident (Fig. 2a, top panel).",
    "Interaction blocks were then introduced.",
    "On each trial, participants first performed the RDK task exactly as described above.",
